= Felicjan Sławoj Składkowski

Składkowski currently serves as Poland’s Minister of Internal Affairs and is a key figure in Józef Piłsudski's Sanacja movement. He prioritizes using state security services to maintain public order and enforce the policies of the post-May Coup government.

